<span class="line"><span>       ├── &#39;,&#39;,&#39; &#39;,&#39;c&#39;,&#39;o&#39;,&#39;u&#39;,&#39;n&#39;,&#39;t&#39;,&#39;=&#39; ──► serial.putc(c)</span></span>
